Class NeoEMFOCLQueryProcessor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeoEMFQueryProcessor

    public class NeoEMFOCLQueryProcessor
extends OCLQueryProcessor
implements NeoEMFQueryProcessor
    A NeoEMF-specific OCLQueryProcessor that computes OCLQuery on top of a NeoEMF resource.

    This class implements NeoEMFQueryProcessor and returns NeoEMFQueryResults that can be reified as regular EObjects.

    Author:
    Gwendal DANIEL
    See Also:
    OCLQuery, OCLQueryProcessor, NeoEMFQueryProcessor, NeoEMFQueryResult

      • process

        public QueryResult process(OCLQuery query,
                           List<ModelDatastore> datastores,
                           Map<String,Object> options)
        Computes a query on the provided datastores with the given options.

        This method is internally called by all the process methods. Override it to change the processing algorithm of the processor.

        Adds an initialization step in the query processing that handles ATL-specific options.

        Overrides:
        process in class OCLQueryProcessor
        Parameters:
        query - the MogwaiQuery to compute
        datastores - the ModelDatastores to compute the query on
        options - a Map containing query execution options
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult wrapping the output of the executed query and allowing EObjects reification
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if datastore is empty or contains more than one datastore, and if the provided ModelDatastore is not an instance of NeoEMFGraphDatastore

      • adaptResult

        protected NeoEMFQueryResult adaptResult(Object result,
                                        GremlinScript gremlinScript,
                                        Map<String,Object> options)
        Adaptes the raw Gremlin engine result and wraps it in a reifiable NeoEMFQueryResult.

        NeoEMFQueryResult can be reified to EObjects if the query returns graph elements corresponding to EObjects (see NeoEMFQueryResult.reifyResults(fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.resource.PersistentResource) ). Standard QueryResult methods can be used to access the raw query results.

        Overrides:
        adaptResult in class AbstractQueryProcessor<OCLQuery>
        Parameters:
        result - the Object representing the output of the Gremlin engine
        script - the computed GremlinScript
        options - a Map containing execution options
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult wrapping the output of the executed script and allowing EObjects reification
        See Also:
        NeoEMFQueryResult.reifyResults(fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.resource.PersistentResource), QueryResult
